 <a  class="img" data-imgtag="<img src=&#39;/worldwide/industry/public_sector/public_safety/images/hero_hurricane_michael_video.png&#39;/>" href="https://youtu.be/DBa37qM0fGY" target="_blank"></a>
 
<p class="title">Hurricane Michael Support</p>

 
<p>See our latest hurricane response efforts.</p>

 
<p><a  class="link" href="https://youtu.be/DBa37qM0fGY" target="_blank">Watch video</a></p>

</div></li>



<li class="hero hasbg containbg"><div>
 <a  class="img" data-imgtag="<img src=&#39;/worldwide/industry/public_sector/public_safety/images/hero_responder_private_core.png&#39;/>" href="https://youtu.be/99s-R9Caq_c" target="_blank"></a>
 
<p class="title">Verizon puts first responders first.</p>

 
<p>In an emergency communication is critical. That’s why we took our world-class network and created a dedicated lane for first responders called Responder Private Core so you can communicate with key personnel even when everyone is calling for help at once. With our many solutions for public safety, we’re helping you do more today and preparing for the future with 5G. From preemption and deployables to priority access, we put first responders first. It's no surprise more first responders rely on us.*</p>

 
<p><a  class="link" href="solutions/responder_private_core_sb.pdf" target="_blank">Learn more</a></p>

