 <a name="overview" title="Overview"></a>
 
<h1>Overview</h1>

 
<h2>Support where it matters, when it matters.</h2>

 
<p>Verizon understands the important role first responders have in protecting and serving our communities and has always been committed to supporting the communication needs of public safety agencies. You can count on our network when you need it most. It's proven to deliver the best performance, especially in times of crisis. Verizon. Response Ready.</p>

 
<p><a  class="linktrack inlink link" href="https://www.verizon.com/about/news-release-categories/emergency-management" target="_blank"> Hurricane Michael updates</a></p>

 
<p><font size="2">*America’s leading wireless voice provider.</font></p>


<article>
<a name="solutions" title="Solutions"></a>
 
<h3>Solutions</h3>

 
<p class="subhead">Delivering the public safety promise.</p>
 
 
<p>We are committed to providing reliable communications for first responders. Learn about how we invest in our network so you can stay connected during a crisis. <br>

 <a  class="linktrack inlink link" href="solutions/10917688_public_safety_network_infographic.pdf" target="_blank"> View Infographic</a></p>

 
<p>We understand public sector needs and offer a breadth of solutions for your specific challenges.</p>



<ul class="c3">


<li><img src="solutions/sol_private_core.png">
<br>


<h3>Responder Private Core</h3>


<p>Your communications are first and secure - no matter what. A dedicated private core that’s available at no additional cost.</p>


<p><a  class="linktrack inlink link" href="solutions/responder_private_core_sb.pdf" target="_blank">Solutions Brief</a></p>

</li>



<li><img src="solutions/sol_preemption.png">
<br>


<h3>Preemption</h3>


<p>Keep first responder communications connected during emergencies, available at no additional cost.</p>


<p><a  class="linktrack inlink link" href="solutions/10923981_SB_PriorityPrevention_V1e_FINAL_chi.pdf" target="_blank">Solutions Brief</a></p>

</li>



<li><img src="solutions/sol_priority_preemption.png">
<br>


<h3>Priority</h3>


<p>Get voice and data priority access when your agency needs it most.</p>


<p><a  class="linktrack inlink link" href="solutions/10923981_SB_MobileBroadband_V1c_FINAL_chi-1.pdf" target="_blank">Mobile Broadband Priority</a><br>

<a  class="linktrack inlink link" href="solutions/10916764_SB_WPS_VoLTE_V1d_FINAL_chi.pdf" target="_blank">Wireless Priority Service</a></p>

</li>


</ul>

<br>



<ul class="c3">


<li><img src="solutions/sol_deployables.png">
<br>


<h3>Deployables</h3>


<p>Verizon Mobile Connectivity Trailer enables rapid communications setup for disaster response.</p>


<p><a  class="linktrack inlink link" href="solutions/10969765_SB_MobileConnectivity_V2b_FINAL_chi.pdf" target="_blank">Solutions Brief</a></p>

</li>



<li><img src="solutions/sol_one_talk.png">
<br>


<h3>One Talk</h3>


<p>One Talk from Verizon gives you one number for both your smartphones and desk phones.</p>


<p><a  class="linktrack inlink link" href="solutions/one_talk_gov_uc.pdf" target="_blank">Use Cases</a></p>

</li>



<li><img src="solutions/sol_ptt.png">
<br>


<h3>Push to Talk</h3>


<p>Instant communication is critical when every second counts while responding to an emergency.</p>


<p><a  class="linktrack inlink link" href="https://enterprise.verizon.com/resources/solutionsbriefs/2018/push_to_talk_plus_overview_solutions_brief_en_xg.pdf" target="_blank">Solutions Brief</a></p>

</li>



</ul>



